word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词，指人们头顶上的天空，一般属于笼罩地球的空气层。较少用于指天国或天堂。
作“天空”解时，常用复数，文学用词；作“天堂”解时，多用大写形式，采用单数。
与heaven同义，宗教色彩浓厚，指好人死后灵魂长存之处，口语中表示乐园或乐事，在宗教典故中，指天主教与基督教中的伊甸乐园。

bilingual.source: And there was something else that didn't go with the idea of heaven in the least.
bilingual.target: 还有一些东西完全不符合天堂的概念。

bilingual.source: This place is as beautiful as heaven.
For her, the garden is her heaven.
bilingual.target: 对她来说，花园就是她的天堂。

bilingual.source: We hope he can rest in peace in heaven.
bilingual.target: 我们希望他能在天堂安息。

bilingual.source: They say that good people go to heaven.
bilingual.target: 他们说，善良的人会去天堂。

bilingual.source: She believes her grandmother is now in heaven.
bilingual.target: 她相信她的祖母现在在天堂。

bilingual.source: She believes that her grandmother is now in heaven.
bilingual.target: 她相信她的祖母现在在天堂。

bilingual.source: The view from the mountain top felt like heaven.
bilingual.target: 从山顶看到的景色感觉像在天堂。

bilingual.source: He prayed every night to go to heaven after he dies.
bilingual.target: 他每晚祈祷死后能去天堂。

bilingual.source: She said that the love she felt was like being in heaven.
bilingual.target: 她说她感受到的爱就像在天堂一样。

list.abstract: heaven（英[ˈhevn]，美[ˈhevn]），英语单词，名词，意思为天堂；天空；神。短语搭配有pennies from heaven（意外的好处；意外之财），例句为“Then he brought fire from heaven to the world.（然后他把火从天堂带到了人间。）” heaven名词类近义词有sky、paradise等。

"Heaven"收录于EmeliSandé的首张专辑《OurVersionofEvents》中，在2011年8月12日作为专辑首支打榜单曲面市发行。单曲灵感是来自于Emeli与制作人NaughtyBoy的一番话。在当今时代，什么都变化的很快。现在的人受了太多影响，也有很多管道去做自己的事，这在Emeli和NaughtyBoy那个时代是很困难的。而NaughtyBoy觉得其实我们只是保持心灵纯净就一切OK了，就是这样的对话让Emeli和NaughtyBoy在半小时内就写好这首歌。这也是他们为专辑写好的第一首歌曲，并且交由KylieMinogue的制作人MikeSpencer制作。

yingyinNormal.en: Then he drowned, and he went to heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来他淹死了，上了天堂。

yingyinNormal.en: Then, there's Outer Space. And nobody knows where's Heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后还有外太空，没有人知道天堂在哪。

yingyinNormal.en: To go to Jewish heaven? Jews don't have heaven. Then to avoid Jewish hell? Have you met my mother? I live in Jewish hell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 死后好上犹太天堂吗？犹太人没有天堂。那是为了避免下犹太地狱吗？你见过我妈吗吧？我不住地狱，谁算住地狱。

yingyinNormal.en: Ma was in a hurry to go boing up to heaven, but she forgot me, Dumbo Ma.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈着急飞往天堂，可她忘了带上我了，傻瓜妈妈。

yingyinNormal.en: No one will remember what you've done, either here on Earth or in your heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人会记住你所做的事，不管是在这人间，还是在你的天堂。

yingyinNormal.en: That is a dot. Your mother is up in heaven going, "Where the hell's my lily, you wuss!"
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是一个点，你妈正在天堂上大叫“我的百合在哪里？你这个懦弱的人”。

yingyinNormal.en: Heaven may be a fantasy for the credulous and the afraid. But I can give you a map reference for hell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天堂或许是轻信者和胆小之人的幻想，但我可以指出地狱的具体地点。

yingyinNormal.en: This is a tattoo of the Earth as seen from a great, great distance. It's the way my mother sees me from heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个刺青是从很远很远的地方看到的地球，我妈从天堂看到我就是这样的。

yingyinNormal.en: Heaven will take you back and look at you and say, Only one thing can make a soul complete, and that thing is love.
yingyinNormal.zh: 连对你敞开怀抱的天堂也会说，只有一样东西能让一个灵魂如此完整，那就是爱情。

yingyinNormal.en: When I was a little older, when I was 17, I was walking home from school. Where was I? You were still up in heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我又长大了一些，在我17岁时，我从学校走回家。那时我在哪儿？你那时还在天堂里。

yingyinNormal.en: This city is shopaholic heaven, and Fifth Avenue with its eye-popping window displays is the high temple of the retail world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个城市贵为购物狂的天堂，第五大道聚集了很多令人心动的品牌商店，是全球租金最昂贵的零售场所。

yingyinNormal.en: From opulent malls to the bustling markets of Temple Street and Ladies Street, tax-free Hong Kong is heaven bargain hunters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从奢华的太古广场到大众化的庙街和女人街，都是购物的热点，而且香港的免税措施是精打细算人士的天堂。

yingyinNormal.en: Absolutely. Really? I mean, not like a heaven where you ride a unicorn all day and live in a mansion made of clouds, but yes, I definitely believe in something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然有。真的吗？并不是说你在天堂能整天骑着独角兽，住在云做的高楼大厦里，但是 我有我的信仰。

yingyinNormal.en: Blue Icees and a trip to The Container Store? It's like I died and went to the post-mortem, neuron-induced hallucination commonly mistaken as heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喝了蓝色冰沙，还去了趟容器大卖场？感觉就像我死了进入了死后脑神经元诱发的幻觉，也就是俗称天堂的地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Manna from heaven. Sweet nectar of life!
yingyinNormal.zh: 上天的赏赐，生活的甜露!

yingyinNormal.en: Heaven and earth? Like in the movie? What?
yingyinNormal.zh: 赴汤蹈火？跟电影里那样？什么？

yingyinNormal.en: You found one? No, that manicure is heaven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你找到了? 不，这种美甲真是太赞了。

yingyinNormal.en: For heaven's sake! Why does everyone keep nagging and nagging?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，为什么大家都来唠叨我。

yingyinNormal.en: What? Why, for heaven's sake? Because I can't let him touch me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？天啊，为什么？因为我没法... 我不能让他碰我。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh for heaven's sake, are we to receive every Bennet in the country?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天哪，乡下所有叫班纳特都来我们家了？

examination_example.sentence: The same curiosity to find what lies beyond the horizon that first brought early Polynesians to Hawaii's shores inspires astronomers today to explore the <highlight>heavens</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 探索地平线以外世界的好奇心最先把早期的波利尼西亚人带到了夏威夷海岸，也正是同样的好奇心激励着当今的天文学家去探索天空。

examination_example.sentence: At issue is the TMT's planned location on Mauna Kea that connects the Hawaiian Islands to the <highlight>heavens</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有争议的是TMT的计划建造地点——连接着夏威夷群岛和天堂的莫纳克亚山。
欧洲不是性别平等的天堂。
